  "texts": [
    "This relationship between the observed frequency, denoted as E f, and the emitted frequency, denoted as E f0, can be described by the following equation:E f = c v ± v r c v ± v s E f0(1)In the above equation, c v represents the propagation speed of waves in the medium.",
    "The term v r denotes the receiver's speed relative to the medium.",
    "If the receiver moves towards the source, v r is added to c v; however, if the receiver moves away from the source, v r is subtracted.",
    "Similarly, v s represents the speed of the source relative to the medium.",
    "If the source moves away from the receiver, v s is added to c v, and v s is subtracted if the source is moving towards the receiver.In this work, we conceptualize humans (humans generating the response) or ChatGPT (ChatGPT generating the response) as sources and consider another human as the observer, as shown in Figure 1."
